	["Timmy told you that he will already have helped you in the future. Go back to Romek."] = "Timmy powiedzial, ze juz pomogl romkowi. Wroc teraz do terazniejszego Romka.",
	["You told romek about Timmy work."] = "Powiedziales romkowi, ze Timmy mu pomogl.",
	["03. Master Baitor"] = "03. Zaneta na karpia",
